## 21. File-by-File Inventory

### Root

- `main.py`: FastAPI app factory, CORS, global exception handler, root/health/readiness endpoints, market-data worker lifecycle.
- `test.py`: small standalone test/helper file.
- `__init__.py`: package marker.
- `Procfile`: deployment command.
- `README.md`: high-level usage and architecture.
- `requirements.txt`: Python dependencies.
- `Backend_Changes_Crypto.md`: recent market-data change log.

### api

- `api/screening.py`: screening API router, request helper models, admin guard, screening routes, details route, worker ops, runtime settings, integration config/history, and gate/entry routes.
- `api/__init__.py`: package marker.

### core

- `core/config.py`: settings class, environment loading, provider normalization, default performance/rate-limit settings, CORS parsing, API key resolution.
- `core/logging_config.py`: logging setup.
- `core/__init__.py`: package marker.

### models

- `models/filters.py`: request-side Pydantic models and validation.
- `models/results.py`: response-side Pydantic models and detail models.
- `models/__init__.py`: package marker.

### services

- `services/asset_router.py`: stock/crypto universe loading, normalization, filtering, manual symbol handling, metadata resolution.
- `services/aroon_oscillator.py`: Aroon compute/evaluate/sticker logic.
- `services/channel_respect.py`: channel touch/respect counting and details.
- `services/confluence.py`: confluence source selection and scenario matching.
- `services/dead_assets.py`: dead-trend detection and omission filter.
- `services/ema.py`: EMA/moving-average rules and stickers.
- `services/gate_session_store.py`: SQLite-backed gate session storage.
- `services/indicators.py`: indicator registry, handlers, snapshot handlers, indicator application engine.
- `services/integration_runtime.py`: runtime integration provider state, history, limits, diagnostics.
- `services/linear_regression_candles.py`: linear-regression candle calculation, evaluation, evidence.
- `services/macd.py`: MACD computation and evaluation.
- `services/market_data.py`: provider clients, timeframes, candle normalization, cache/live fetches, grouped daily/snapshot paths, Binance support, fundamentals attachment.
- `services/market_data_store.py`: SQLite cache/interest/indicator-cache store.
- `services/market_data_worker.py`: background cache warmer and refresh scheduler.
- `services/pine_math.py`: Pine-compatible numeric functions.
- `services/regression_channels.py`: LRC and DW regression channels.
- `services/rsi.py`: RSI calculation and evaluation.
- `services/screener.py`: main screening orchestration and response construction.
- `services/stock_reference.py`: stock metadata enrichment, sector/category mapping, stock universe filters.
- `services/stock_session.py`: TradingView regular-session filtering for stock intraday candles.
- `services/trend_channels.py`: trend channel computation and area evaluation.
- `services/trendy_adx.py`: ADX/DI computation and rule evaluation.
- `services/utils.py`: shared candle math, formatting, pattern, touch, and confirmation helpers.
- `services/vlr.py`: Volume Linear Regression indicator.
- `services/volume.py`: volume spike logic.
- `services/wavetrend.py`: WaveTrend indicator.
- `services/__init__.py`: package marker.

### validation

- `validation/alignment.py`: candle/result alignment helpers.
- `validation/comparison.py`: generic comparison helpers.
- `validation/spec.py`: validation specifications.
- `validation/fixture_store.py`: validation fixture storage.
