- `validation/twelve/client.py`: Twelve Data client.
- `validation/twelve/candles.py`: Twelve candle handling.
- `validation/twelve/common.py`: shared Twelve helpers.
- `validation/twelve/rsi.py`, `macd.py`, `ema.py`, `aroon.py`: Twelve indicator logic.
